(562, 'UFCW 648 Shop Steward', NULL, '<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;"><img alt="" src="http://ufcw5.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Screen-Shot-2015-03-16-at-2.23.16-PM.png" style="width: 280px; height: 146px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">Good stewards are the backbone of an effective union.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">Good stewards are the backbone of an effective union. We reach out to new members and help educate them on their rights. We serve as a bridge between elected union leadership and workers on the job. We listen to our co-workers and provide a confidential way for members to bring forward their ideas and concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="margin: 0.75em 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 20px; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">But most importantly, it is a steward&rsquo;s job to inspire, lead and build a sense of unity and solidarity among the wide range of workers in our union.</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">All union members have a right to have their steward present with them during meetings that they feel might be disciplinary. In 1975, in NLRB v. J. Weingarten, Inc, the U.S. Supreme Court upheld the rights of employees to have union representation during investigatory interviews. Since that case involved a clerk being investigated by the Weingarten Company, these rights have become known as&nbsp;<a href="http://www.ufcw.org/resources/stewards/weingarten-rights/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(60, 90, 152); text-decoration: none;" title="Weingarten Rights">&ldquo;Weingarten rights.&rdquo;</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">If you are called into a closed meeting with your manager and you start to feel nervous that things may take a disciplinary turn, you have the right to stop the meeting and request the meeting be resumed when your union steward is present. If you&rsquo;ve got questions about your contract, your steward is the best person to ask.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;"><img alt="" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-13945" height="318" src="http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/organize.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto 15px; padding: 0px; outline: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: auto; display: block; float: none;" title="organize" width="620" />‚Äã</p>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 13:20:36', '20.1', 4, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1),
(563, 'Learn about YOUR candidates. Make a change in YOUR community.', NULL, '<p><strong>Our Mission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="padding-right: 0px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding-left: 5px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To increase political involvement among the membership of the various Labor Unions<a href="http://www.afl-cio.org/" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(3, 112, 234);" target="mainFrame" title="">&nbsp;</a>affiliated with the Santa Clara &amp; San Benito Building &amp; Construction Trades Council<a href="http://www.scbtc.org/" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(3, 112, 234);" target="_blank" title="">&nbsp;</a>and the South Bay Labor Council.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To inform working people by providing them information from various sources.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To create a resource for historical, current<a href="http://www.laborvote.com/current.htm" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(3, 112, 234);" target="mainFrame" title="">&nbsp;</a>and future<a href="http://www.laborvote.com/future.htm" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(3, 112, 234);" target="mainFrame" title="">&nbsp;</a>issues that directly and indirectly impact working families in our community.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To focus on issues that directly affect the lives of our members, working families and residents of this great community.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To register to vote as many working families as possible in an effort to support and further the causes of those who Labor for a living.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '2015-04-09 07:57:13', '11.3', 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
