(572, '', NULL, '<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;"><img alt="" class="wp-image-489 aligncenter" src="http://fajjemobile.info/ufcwunitedlatinos.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/862687_592774410750016_136361103_n3.jpg" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; height: 200px; display: block; width: 280px;" title="Latinos in Action 2013" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div id="hdr" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(0, 37, 87); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow: hidden; background: rgb(0, 73, 144);">\r\n<header class="wrapper" id="hdr-content" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; max-width: 980px;">\r\n<h1 class="pagetitle" style="line-height: 1em; margin: 0px 12px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left;">United Latinos of UFCW</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="post" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">\r\n<div class="entry" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png) 0% 22px no-repeat;"><em>Working Toward Latino Empowerment and Building Latino Pride!</em></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">The United Latinos of the United Food and Commercial Workers Union (UFCW) is an organization of men and women who have joined together to promote the issues and pursue interests important to Latino workers.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">&ldquo;Working Toward Latino Empowerment and Building Latino Pride!&rdquo; We have a simple but powerful purpose of empowering Latino men and women within the UFCW and within our communities. We are also building Latino pride which will help others better understand our cultural differences. Our diversity will help make our organization and our society stronger. The United Latinos will help teach others that through UFCW membership, there is a better way of life that includes wages, health benefits, pensions, job security and dignity.</strong></p>\r\n', '', '2015-05-19 10:28:10', '3