30px; background: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png) 0% 22px no-repeat;"><em>We are here to help!</em></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>United Latinos will assist UFCW Regions, Local Unions and other&nbsp;organzsations in their efforts to communicate, organize and servicing Latino members. We help with basic Spanish translations, Spanish&nbsp;press conferences and rallies, organizing (blitz and campaigns), immigration issues, help in training programs for Latino workers, voter registration, GOTV, electing candidates etc.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>The United Latinos&nbsp;is the face and the voice of the UFCW when we need to reach Latino working men&nbsp;and women.</div>\r\n', '', '2015-05-19 10:29:24', '32.4', 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1),
