(613, '', NULL, '<h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">Shop Union and&nbsp;Patronize Union Workplaces</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">The following is a list of UFCW 99 Union workplaces. When you choose to patronize a union workplace, you are making&nbsp;<a href="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/9774249_1.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(56, 56, 56); text-decoration: none;"><img alt="9774249_1" class="alignright  wp-image-149" height="202" src="http://ufcw648.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/9774249_1-300x252.jpg" style="margin: 5px 0px 15px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; height: auto; float: right;" width="240" /></a>a&nbsp;choice to support your community and a better quality of life for the people who live there. By having a voice in the workplace, union members can improve working conditions for ourselves and the people we serve every day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Grocery and Meat</strong><br />\r\n<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Retail</strong><br />\r\n<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Health Care</strong><br />\r\n<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Other Industries</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 50); line-height: 1.6; font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Why Patronizing Union Matters</h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 24.8888893127441px;">Union members, on average get paid more in wages, get better health benefits, vacation, sick leave and retirement plan than non-union members. And union members have a contract with their employer that helps protects them from favoritism and unjust treatment on the job.<br />\r\nAs a customer or patient, where you choose to spend your money and get your health care sends a message. Thank you for choosing a union workplace when shopping. It makes a difference.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">Shop Union Directory</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: normal;">To Come</p>\r\n', '', '2015-04-01 20:03:16', '59', 7, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
