(620, '', NULL, '<p><img alt="" src="http://www.linkedunion.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Screen-Shot-2015-04-01-at-5.01.36-PM.png" style="width: 280px; height: 57px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div id="hdr" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(0, 37, 87); font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow: hidden; background: rgb(0, 73, 144);">\r\n<header class="wrapper" id="hdr-content" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; max-width: 980px;">\r\n<h1 class="pagetitle" style="line-height: 1em; margin: 0px 12px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left;">UFCW Local 99</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="post" style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 20.7999992370605px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="entry" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<h2 style="line-height: 1em; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">Support UFCW Local 99 Shops</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;">Without doubt one great advantage of being a union member is better than average wages and benefits. And without doubt, when workers earn good wages the entire community benefits. Good income means there is more money to spend throughout the community and workers with good incomes are not dependent on government subsidies or public health services.</span><br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;" />\r\n<br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;">Because union workers on average earn anywhere from 20% to 40% more in hourly wages than non-union, and have superior health and welfare benefits, their spending power is stronger. And in a community a where residents have good incomes better businesses and services are attracted to the community. Therefore, shopping at union stores not only benefits the employee but the local community as a whole.</span><br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;" />\r\n<br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;" />\r\n<strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: 19.2000007629395px;">Support your communities by shopping at the following Local 99&nbsp;businesses:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.aceparking.com/2011/03/ace-parking-management-becomes-the-largest-parking-management-operator-in-phoenix/">Ace Parking - Phoenix</a><br />\r\n<a href="http://www.aceparking.com/2011/03/ace-parking-management-becomes-the-largest-parking-management-operator-in-phoenix/">Ace Parking - Tucson</a><br />\r\n<a href="http://www.albertsons.com/pd/stores/AZ/Yuma/Yuma-24th-Street-and-Avenue-B/B6B278459">Albertson&#39;s - Yuma</a><br />\r\n<a href="https://www.alsco.com/en/index.htm">ALSCO</a><br />\r\n<a href="http://www.acdl.com/">Arizona Center for Disability Law</a><br />\r\n<a href="https://www.desertmuseum.org/">Arizona Sonora Desert Museum</a><br />\r\n<a href="http://www.bensonhospital.org/index.php/en/">Benson Hospital</a><br />\r\n<a href="http://www.arizona-businessdirectory.com/company-calcot-compress_204029">Calcot Compress Company</a><br />\r\n<a href="http://www.clsaz.org/site/">Community Legal Service</a><br />\r\n', '', '2015-08-31 15:12:37', '51.5', 7, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
(621, '', NULL, '<p><img alt="" src="http://www.linkedunion.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Screen-Shot-2015-04-01-at-5.01.36-PM.png" style="width: 280px; height: 57px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="3" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;" width="100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor="#2D2A6E" class="style14" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold;" valign="top">BALANCE FOR LIFE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="top">\r\n			<table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="5" width="100%">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" valign="middle" width="31%">&nbsp;</td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><big>The UFCW &amp; Employers Arizona Health Plan is pleased to bring to you the Balance for Life Wellness &amp; Health Education Programs. The focus on wellness today is education and prevention. Your Balance for Life Program will design a Personal Action Plan. A Wellness Coach and/or Nurse Educator will work with you and your health care professionals to define personalized, easy to follow goals. It can be fun too!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>It&#39;s Easy to Access all your Wellness &amp; Health Education Opportunities!<br />\r\n&bull; Empower healthy people with the skills and knowledge to stay healthy!<br />\r\n&bull; Guide and support plan participants who have health needs and questions!<br />\r\n&bull; Provide immediate assistance for those with chronic health issues to keep their health condition symptoms from worsening!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Call toll free: 866-273-8618 or <a href="http://www.balanceforlifeaz.com/">sign up online.</a></big></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="3" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;" width="100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor="#2D2A6E" valign="top"><span class="style24" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>MEDICAL and HOSPITAL</strong></span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<p><big>You have a choice of PPO Coverage or an individualized indemnity program. Other benefits include maternity coverage, emergency care and coverage for major medical. Claims are processed by a professional firm of administrators and paid out of the union&#39;s trust funds.</big></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor="#2D2A6E" class="style14" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold;" valign="top">DENTAL and ORTHODONTIC</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<p class="style2"><big>20% discount or no out of pocket expense (depending on your plan coverage, not exceeding the maximum plan benefit and provided you have coverage for the month of services.</big></p>\r\n\r\n			<p class="style2"><big>For Union members without coverage, a 20% discount will be given off of the total visit charge.</big></p>\r\n\r\n			<p class="style2"><big>For a list of providers who discount or waive &quot;out-of-pocket&quot; costs to Union members, contact the Union office.</big></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor="#2D2A6E" class="style14" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold;" valign="top">CHIROPRACTIC</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="style2" valign="top">\r\n			<p><big>Members and their families receive high-quality chiropractic (spine-related) either fully paid or at substantially reduced prices.</big></p>\r\n\r\n			<p><big>For a list of Chiropractice providers who discount or waive &quot;out-of-pocket&quot; costs to Union members, contact the Union office.</big></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td bgcolor="#2D2A6E" class="style14" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: bold;" valign="top">PRESCRIPTION DRUGS</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<p><big><font color="#000000">Paid prescription coverage is our most-used b