(738, 'Verde Canyon Railway', 'Clarkdale, Arizona', '<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">The Verde Canyon Railroad is often referred to as the finest train ride in Arizona and acclaimed as Arizona&rsquo;s longest-running nature show.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">The remote wilderness of the Verde Canyon, located west of Sedona and below Jerome, is renowned for its towering red rock pinnacles and clean, green waters. The train rolls past Indian ruins, through a 680-foot man-made tunnel, over old-fashioned trestles and under clear azure skies. This picturesque setting is further enhanced by the variety of indigenous flora and fauna and the many migrating waterfowl. Over thirty bald and golden eagles winter in this riparian respite each year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Passengers enjoy this four-hour scenic train ride in first-class style aboard renovated passenger coaches and open-air viewing cars pulled by vintage locomotives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">The Verde Canyon is often called &#39;Arizona&rsquo;s other Grand Canyon&#39; with spectacular canyon scenery on a train trip that offers visual feasts including seasonal spring flowers, fall foliage and hundreds of migratory birds, such as the majestic bald eagle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;"><span class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">10% discount off of any class, any time of the year. Can be booked as a package with</span>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.blazinm.com/" style="color: rgb(25, 32, 103);" target="_blank">Blazin&#39; M Ranch Chuckwagon dinner show</a>.</p>\r\n', '', '2015-11-21 12:20:22', '61', 7, 'c41e7d0328.png', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
(739, 'Universal Studios Hollywood', 'Southern California', '<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Find a full day of action-packed entertainment all in one place.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">With thrilling park rides and shows, a real working movie studio and L.A&#39;s best shops, restaurants and all-new cinemas at CityWalk, Universal Studios Hollywood is a unique experience that&#39;s fun for the whole family.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">\r\n	<li>Witness real sets from some of your favorite movies on the world famous Studio Tour.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience hair-raising thrills and heart-pounding surprises on rides like the Revenge of the Mummy thrill coaster and the Jurassic Park 80-foot raft plunge.</li>\r\n	<li>Finish your day off at Universal CityWalk, where there&#39;s always way more new and way more to do.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Plus 2 days FREE:<br />\r\nAdult/Child - $84.00 (gate price $95.00 - you save $11.00)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTickets can be purchased at the Union office. (on-line purchase)</p>\r\n', '', '2015-11-21 12:22:11', '61', 7, '7a3f5f392e.png', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
(740, 'National Car Rental', 'Visit our website or call 1-800-CAR-RENT√Ç¬Æ to save today!', '<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">As a UFCW Local 99 member,&nbsp;<span class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">you&rsquo;ll receive unlimited mileage and discounts of up to 20%&nbsp;</span>off National&rsquo;s rates at approximately 3,000 locations in 72 countries across the globe. National also offers UFCW Local 99 members a complimentary membership in the Emerald Club, National&rsquo;s frequent renter program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Visit our website or call 1-800-CAR-RENT&reg; to save today! Be sure to call the Union office and request the Contract I.D. number to receive your discount.</p>\r\n', '', '2015-11-21 10:27:47', '62', 7, '111c89f0bd.png', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
(741, 'Good Year Gemini Auto Care ', 'Contact the Union office for instructions on how to get your discount coupon.', '<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Regular car maintenance and new tire purchases help stretch the longevity and value of your vehicle. Now, when you use the Union Plus Goodyear Discounts, you can help keep your car in good shape and save money - while also supporting your fellow union members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Many Goodyear tires are made by members of the United Steelworkers of America (USW) and the United Food and Commercial Workers (UFCW). Through an agreement with the company-owned Goodyear Gemini Auto Service Centers, Union Plus Goodyear discount tires and car service deals are now available exclusively to union members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Cash in on the following special union-member-only deals for Goodyear discount tires and more:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">5% off all Goodyear tires, including car tires, snow tires, all-terrain and more</li>\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">10% service - including sale prices</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;"><strong>Contact the Union office for instructions on how to get your discount coupon.</strong></p>\r\n', '', '2015-11-21 10:35:23', '63', 7, '72be87f4f0.png', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
(742, 'Van Chevrolet Buick GMC', 'Union members must contact Michael Benson at (480)348-8356 or Bob Mooney at (623) 512-5332 to receive any of the above Union discounts.', '<ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">GM supplier pricing on any Chevrolet Buick GMC - below invoice plus any rebates (Exclusions: Corvette and specialty cars)</li>\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">No dealer adds charges</li>\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Free door edge guards</li>\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">20% off all parts and accessories</li>\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">FREE window tinting</li>\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Two years of FREE scheduled maintenance - oil changes and tire rotations with the purchase of any new car, truck, or SUV</li>\r\n	<li class="style15" style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Service loaners for Union members: scheduled appointments preset with &quot;service advisor union contact&quot; will receive a free service loaner on availability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">Union members must contact Michael Benson at (480)348-8356 or Bob Mooney at (623) 512-5332 to receive any of the above Union discounts.</p>\r\n', '', '2015-11-20 17:44:09', '64', 7, '6e49464ee8.png', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 1),
